title: Maxwell Technologies Schedules Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call for October 29, 2015
text: Maxwell Technologies Schedules Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call for October 29, 2015   Published on 2015-10-15 13:45:28 Maxwell Technologies Schedules Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call for... -- SAN DIEGO, Oct.   Enabling Energy's Future. Enabling Energy's Future.  ><- stripped tags -> SAN DIEGO , Oct.   Maxwell Technologies, Inc. (NASDAQ: [[]]) announced today that it plans to release financial and operational results for the third quarter 2015, after market close on Thursday, October 29, 2015 . Following the release, Maxwell management will host a conference call with live webcast to discuss these results. Other forward-looking and material information may also be discussed during this call. Conference call details: Date: Thursday, October 29, 2015 Time: 5:00 p.m. EST / 2:00 p.m. PST Domestic dial-in number: 1-877-876-9174 International dial-in number: 1-785-424-1669 Conference ID: MAXWELL The conference call, webcast and subsequent archived replay may be accessed via the following link: [[UEdFZ2NtVnNQVndpYm05bWIyeHNiM2RjSWlCdmJtTnNhV05yUFNkc2FXNXJUMjVEYkdsamF5aDBhR2x6S1NjZ2FISmxaajFjSW1oMGRIQTZMeTlwYm5abGMzUnZjbk11YldGNGQyVnNiQzVqYjIwdlhDSWdjbVZzUFZ3aWJtOW1iMnhzYjNkY0lpQjBZWEpuWlhROVhDSmZZbXhoYm10Y0lqNW9kSFJ3T2k4dmFXNTJaWE4wYjNKekxtMWhlSGRsYkd3dVkyOXRQQzloUGc9PXw=]]. About Maxwell: Maxwell is a global leader in the development and manufacture of innovative, cost-effective energy storage and power delivery solutions. Our ultracapacitor products provide safe and reliable power solutions for applications in consumer and industrial electronics, transportation and telecommunications. Our high-voltage grading and coupling capacitors help to ensure the safety and reliability of electric utility infrastructure and other applications involving transport, distribution and measurement of high-voltage electrical energy. Our radiation-mitigated microelectronic products include power modules, memory modules and single board computers that incorporate powerful commercial silicon for superior performance and high reliability in aerospace applications.
